("Delhi haat","Delhi","Food Streets","https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhN4PrsSVuCXq0UmKRdzrahsxTRC1fGi3UFHwI2kd0pRATNUYtf8tqT-Hcq-AftfC0U9nkADBEbNhzWoWtwMniqvXhwENqMessNX45JLwtnK37qieO1N4ZC3GqlIufXl_I14d9UA1OQnUAu/s1600/IMG_1488.jpg","https://www.delhitourism.gov.in/tourist_place/dilli_haat_INA.html","Delhi Haat is a flavorful journey across India : where every bite brings a new state to your plate. From Rajasthani thalis to Momos from the Northeast, every stall serves up authentic regional flavors. Its the perfect mix of yummy food, artsy vibes, and chill hangouts!"),
