("Worlds of Wonder","Delhi","Amusement/Theme Parks","https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ9_-Tc33o95D0y4N8guFi48FhsX3hQpDC58w&s","https://www.worldsofwonder.in/","Hey thrill-seeker! Ready for a full day of fun? Worlds of Wonder has it all : crazy rides, water slides, wave pool, and endless excitement! Perfect for friends, family, and that much-needed break from routine! "),
("Atlantic Water World","Delhi","Amusement/Theme Parks","https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTBjb9NH6R4T1_bTy8zHvHRIR1nmLwBKVQo8g&s","https://www.atlanticwaterworld.com/","Hey water lover! Dive into the fun at Atlantic Water World : packed with thrilling slides, lazy river, wave pool, and splash zones! A perfect chill spot for summer fun with friends & family! "),
("Adventure Island","Delhi","Amusement/Theme Parks","https://media1.thrillophilia.com/filestore/76o7oumz25aegil5ic41zlk7hboq_1575441451_adventure-island_onlinecake.in.jpg?w=400&dpr=2","https://www.thrillophilia.com/attractions/adventure-island","Hey adventurer! Looking for a fun escape? Amusement/Theme Parks are packed with thrilling rides, fun games, yummy snacks, and endless laughter. Perfect for a day out with friends, fam, or even a cute date! "),
("Fun N Food","Delhi","Amusement/Theme Parks","https://static.toiimg.com/thumb/47972514/FunnFood-Village.jpg?width=1200&height=900","https://www.funnfoodparks.com/","Hey fun-lover!  Want rides and water slides in one place? Fun N Food Village has it all : high-speed water rides, wave pool, and classic amusement park fun. Great for a splashy day out with friends or family! "),
("Dlf Avenue","Delhi","Movie Theatres","https://www.scai.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/DLF-Avenue-Facade-Shot.jpeg","https://www.dlfavenue.com/","Movie night? This is the spot! Catch the latest blockbusters in style at PVR ECX, then chill with great food, coffee, or desserts : all right here at DLF Avenue Saket. Perfect for your weekend scenes! "),
("Pacific Mall","Delhi","Movie Theatres","https://static.toiimg.com/photo/47895239.cms","https://www.pacificmalls.in/tagore-garden.","Movie buff? Hit up Pacific Mall s sleek multiplex:think comfy recliners, Dolby Atmos sound, and the latest blockbusters on big screens. Grab your popcorn and nachos, then settle in for the ultimate cinema experience! "),
("Majnu ka Tila","Delhi","Hidden Gems","https://www.jagranimages.com/images/newimg/24062022/24_06_2022-majnu_ka_tila_22831735.webp","https://www.zomato.com/hi/ncr/majnu-ka-tila-delhi-restaurants","Hey wanderer! Step into a mini-Tibet at Majnu Ka Tila : narrow lanes, cozy cafes, momos, thukpa, and chill vibes all around. Perfect for foodies, shoppers, and Insta explorers! "),
("Sunder Nursery Park","Delhi","Hidden Gems","https://thepatriot.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sunder-Nursery-1-e1719925233489.jpg","https://www.sundernursery.org/home.php","Hey nature lover! Need a peaceful escape? Sunder Nursery is your green getaway : lush gardens, Mughal vibes, cute picnic spots, and perfect photo corners. Ideal for morning walks or chill dates! "),
("Dlf","Delhi","Shopping Malls","https://static.toiimg.com/photo/59769969.cms","https://www.dlfmallofindia.com/.","Hey shopaholic! Ready for next-level fun? DLF Mall of India has 300+ brands, a huge food court, multiplex cinema, and even an indoor play zone. Perfect for shopping sprees, food hunts, and movie nights!"),
("Select City Walk","Delhi","Shopping Malls","https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/photo/61719933.cms","https://www.zomato.com/ncr/restaurants/in/select-city-walk-mall-saket.","Hey trendsetter! Select CITYWALK is your go-to for premium shopping, cute cafes, open-air vibes, and luxury brands. Whether it s a shopping day, movie plan, or chill evening : this place hits the spot! "),
